These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, collecting
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, social-worker
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, epic
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, colombian
2 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
2. the social-worker is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the owner of the hamster is the colombian##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk     | hot-chocolate       |
| Hobby         | reading   | collecting     |
| Job           | freelancer | social-worker   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | comedy  |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai |
| Pet           | hamster      | ferret     |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | scooter   |

