.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, cooking
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, gospel
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, french
2 different pets are kept: snake, dog
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, bike
1. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the owner of the dog is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
4. the french is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby         | cooking        | photography  |
| Job           | lawyer | security-guard  |
| Music-Genre   | gospel            | electronic    |
| Nationality   | argentine     | french   |
| Pet           | snake         | dog    |
| Transport     | scooter           | bike      |

